  "detailed_description": "<h1>Roadmap</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346950/extras/145572b16b0838fc16e0a260d0696066.poster.avif?t=1773453762\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346950/extras/145572b16b0838fc16e0a260d0696066.webm?t=1773453762\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346950/extras/145572b16b0838fc16e0a260d0696066.mp4?t=1773453762\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The DLC is made in the Quest genre, where you will be able to:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Travel through 5 locations of KD Corp<br></li><li>Paint 16 new pictures<br></li><li>Unravel the mystery of the recipe for a new chip flavor<br></li><li>Talk to and help 3 new characters<br></li><li>Encounter and discover special events</li></ul><br>This is a free DLC that will be released as a patch.  <br>All game owners will receive it automatically.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Thank you <3</h2><br>I’m grateful that you play, like, write reviews, and share my game.  <br><br>Only thanks to your support did I decide to make this DLC, and thanks to you it is already better than before.  <br><br>P.S. With love, Kirillov Dmitrii by Kirillov Production<br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346950/extras/c9c90995c59f5493710bf5cd848caf95.poster.avif?t=1773453762\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346950/extras/c9c90995c59f5493710bf5cd848caf95.webm?t=1773453762\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346950/extras/c9c90995c59f5493710bf5cd848caf95.mp4?t=1773453762\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A unique story about Sanechek, the kitten-girl</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help the kitten recover her lost coins so she can enjoy onion, paprika, or maybe just classic chips again?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346950/extras/1fb37ceec53d52cf73c33e9e0eb16e98.poster.avif?t=1773453762\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346950/extras/1fb37ceec53d52cf73c33e9e0eb16e98.webm?t=1773453762\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346950/extras/1fb37ceec53d52cf73c33e9e0eb16e98.mp4?t=1773453762\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Decide fate</strong>: 2 endings – can you earn enough for a bag of chips?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Empathize</strong>: an engaging story that won’t leave you indifferent.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Go to work</strong>: 5 unique jobs, each with its own mechanics and endings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346950/extras/c201a826f8fcf7da948dd5304433172a.poster.avif?t=1773453762\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346950/extras/c201a826f8fcf7da948dd5304433172a.webm?t=1773453762\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346950/extras/c201a826f8fcf7da948dd5304433172a.mp4?t=1773453762\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Paint</strong>: solve puzzles to create artwork.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Watch</strong>: cinematic cutscenes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Listen</strong>: enjoy immersive soundtracks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Duration</strong>: ~1–2 hours.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346950/extras/d60d02f970c47b630c4b5ccdf285b978.poster.avif?t=1773453762\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346950/extras/d60d02f970c47b630c4b5ccdf285b978.webm?t=1773453762\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346950/extras/d60d02f970c47b630c4b5ccdf285b978.mp4?t=1773453762\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is an indie project by a solo developer who created this game in a short time to tell a story based on a real character.</p>",
